# Agent Communication Contract

## AgentRequest Schema

```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["agent", "session_id", "trace_id", "context", "request"],
  "properties": {
    "agent": {
      "type": "string",
      "enum": ["orchestrator", "assessment", "planning", "tutor", "quiz", "feedback"]
    },
    "session_id": {
      "type": "string",
      "format": "uuid"
    },
    "trace_id": {
      "type": "string",
      "format": "uuid"
    },
    "context": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "profile": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "student_id": {
              "type": "string",
              "format": "uuid"
            },
            "name": {
              "type": "string"
            },
            "knowledge_level": {
              "type": "string",
              "enum": ["beginner", "intermediate", "advanced"]
            },
            "learning_preferences": {
              "type": "object"
            }
          }
        },
        "plan": {
          "type": "object"
        },
        "conversation": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "role": {
                "type": "string",
                "enum": ["user", "agent"]
              },
              "content": {
                "type": "string"
              },
              "timestamp": {
                "type": "string",
                "format": "date-time"
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "request": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": ["action"],
      "properties": {
        "action": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "payload": {
          "type": "object"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

## AgentResponse Schema

```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["status", "agent", "data", "next_state", "context_updates"],
  "properties": {
    "status": {
      "type": "string",
      "enum": ["success", "partial", "failed"]
    },
    "agent": {
      "type": "string",
      "enum": ["orchestrator", "assessment", "planning", "tutor", "quiz", "feedback"]
    },
    "data": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "lesson_text": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "exercise": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "tavily_results": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "title": {"type": "string"},
              "url": {"type": "string"},
              "summary": {"type": "string"},
              "domain": {"type": "string"}
            }
          }
        },
        "question": {
          "type": "object"
        },
        "score": {
          "type": "number"
        }
      }
    },
    "next_state": {
      "type": "string",
      "enum": ["GREETING", "ASSESSING", "PLANNING", "LEARNING", "QUIZZING", "REMEDIATING", "FEEDBACK"]
    },
    "context_updates": {
      "type": "object"
    }
  }
}
```

## Agent-Specific Endpoints

### Assessment Agent
- **Action**: `start`
- **Input**: Empty payload
- **Output**: Begins 5-question assessment flow

### Tutor Agent
- **Action**: `teach`
- **Input**: Topic to teach
- **Output**: Lesson content with intro, explanation, example, exercise

### Quiz Agent
- **Input**: Topic to quiz on
- **Output**: Quiz question with hint support